    "body": "## What\nAdds draft BIP360 P2MR support plumbing across validation/policy/type handling and tests.\n\n## Scope\n- witness v2 P2MR validation path in script interpreter\n- policy/standardness handling for P2MR spends\n- `WITNESS_V2_P2MR` type plumbing updates\n- functional test `feature_p2mr.py` and related unit test updates\n\n## Test Coverage\n- `ctest --output-on-failure -j6`\n- targeted functional tests including `feature_p2mr.py`, `feature_taproot.py`, mempool package tests\n- `test_runner.py --extended --jobs=6`\n- compatibility/tool tests requiring extra build/release artifacts\n",
